cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software in your research, please cite it using the metadata below."
type: software
title: "Container Risk Factsheet"
abstract: >
  A Python tool and REST API for generating Container Security Risk Factsheets from Docker
  Compose files. It analyses a deployment's security posture by extracting deployment traits,
  evaluating security assumptions against the CSRO ontology, matching a context scenario,
  and identifying possible attack actions. A treatment report command groups risk remediation
  actions by severity (Critical → High → Moderate → Low).
